message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with sound separation, which is a subfield of audio signal processing. Other likely categories could be cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper uses visual data in conjunction with sound, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper proposes a novel framework for sound separation using deep learning, cs.SI (sound and music computing) as the paper deals with sound processing, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper deals with both visual and audio data.
